title: Totally Trippin' (1995) [MP3 192Kbps]
description:
A nice present from my sister, back in 1995. Didn't like CD1 but CD2 has some *serious* gems, like track 4, 7 and 10. 
My favorite track still remains "Source Experience - Point Zero" on CD2. For me, it didn't lose any of its energy and dreamy character, even after celebrating its 20 year anniversary. This was one of the reasons I wanted to share it with the community. Enjoy!
